data.description: Sometimes you get the land, sometimes you get the Lake. Well how about both!? 1.78 acres with over 430 feet of water front on High Rock Lake in Salisbury! Tucked back in Crane Cove you'll find privacy and seclusion on your own piece of lake front property. A perfect setting to create your own dream paradise or settle down in a custom built brick home. Inside the home you'll find over 3300 square feet of living space, soaring ceilings, large bedrooms and eat in kitchen. Locust wood walls and ceiling beams in the living room, stone fire place, custom windows, and a screened in patio to watch the sunset are just a few of the many eye catching features. Home also has a newly installed roof (2023), multi zoned HVAC (2020), and encapsulated basement crawl space. Can't forget the Lake Life Amenities! High Rock is known for it's fishing, boating and its expansive shore line (2nd largest lake in NC). With million dollar homes being sold on the lake, this is a must see opportunity!
